438
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:08,800
Ji Ruofeng, I don't know if my master has truly lost his skills.

439
00:43:08,800 --> 00:43:12,100
But you definitely have no tact.

440
00:43:15,180 --> 00:43:17,300
I taught you the Autumn Water Technique.

441
00:43:17,300 --> 00:43:20,300
- Are you confident you can beat me? 
 - Don't be too confident.

442
00:43:20,300 --> 00:43:22,400
My master is Li Changsheng now.

443
00:43:22,400 --> 00:43:25,800
Plus the Xichu's Sword Song was taught to me by the Scholarly Diety.

